ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:18:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://vignette4.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/a/aa/35736_476792358008_831763008_6129412_2944023_n.jpg/revision/latest\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette4.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fa%2Faa%2F35736_476792358008_831763008_6129412_2944023_n.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest&h=829536e2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n而家Wikia想點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開post量？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先,屌臭asso ive o 既風氣,由4月尾至6月中會達至高峰，<br />\n因為班AL面對放榜壓力無從發洩 <br />\n要搵人黎踩下定下個心 <br />\n6月中後會突然水盡鵝飛 <br />\n一黎怕自己會入，留條後路 <br />\n二黎開始迷信，想積下口德 <br />\n<br />\nAL放榜後，愁雲慘霧 <br />\n班CE仔見狀都唔敢亂屌 <br />\n所以由6月尾至8月 <br />\n情況相若，風氣極低位橫行，如經濟衰退一樣 <br />\n<br />\n到9月，開學兩三禮拜，新一屆AL CE仔開始有壓力，想搵人踩 <br />\nretake緊o既又想有野俾佢增強信心，又踩 <br />\n讀緊asso ive 跟唔上o個班/讀得唔開心o既，又踩 <br />\n因此9月會有個小陽春，之後橫行，<br />\n12月至1月頭，同2月中，分別都會有個小陽春，因為有假放得閒，同考試迫近，<br />\n壓力愈來愈大，3月至4月頭會一直高位橫行 <br />\n<br />\n最後又到4月尾高峰 <br />\n年年都如是，歲歲皆如此 <br />\n<br />\n股市係咁就好囉屌你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係未睇過嘛"},{"pid":"ef3758f0c4e6ebc4da78ffb4e5bfde6564774d23","tid":262982,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今時今日去台灣google下就大把教學 班友懶到<br />\n送埋入口<br />\n<br />\nBtw 依家去日本同去台灣洗費差唔多 寧願去日本</blockquote><br />\n住同食已經差好遠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去東京洗費比台北多幾倍喎..</blockquote><br />\n我東京 台北  大阪<br />\n都係用得5000左右<br />\n<br />\n可能我唔大洗"},{"pid":"7030754d52a151cfdf26a8a3224ba05d5fd6266f","tid":262982,"uid":11236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:36:16.000Z"